'''Alexia Uwera Mupende''' (17 Ugushyingo 1984 - 8 Mutarama 2019) yari umunyamideli [[Rwanda|w’umunyarwandakazi]], umukinnyi w’amafirime n’inzobere mu bijyanye n’isiporo rusange z'ifasha umubiri, igihe yapfaga, yari umuyobozi mukuru muri ''Waka Fitness'', i [[Kigali]], umurwa mukuru w’u [[Rwanda]]. <ref name="1R">http://www.pmldaily.com/news/2019/01/mystery-as-rwandan-model-actress-alexia-mupende-is-stabbed-to-death-by-maid.html</ref>

== Amavu n'amavuko ==
Alexia Uwera yavukiye muri [[Kenya]] . Yize amashuri muri [[Ubugande|Uganda]], ahabwa impamyabumenyi y'amashuri makuru muri Namasagali College mu Karere ka Kamuli . Yakomeje kubona impamyabumenyi y'amashuri yisumbuye muri St. Lawrence College, muri [[Uganda]]. Nyuma yibyo yimukiye mu [[Rwanda]] aho yarangirije impamyabumenyi ya Bachelor of Information Technology  yakuye muri [[kaminuza y'u Rwanda]] . <ref name="1R" /><ref>https://www.isimbi.rw/imideli/article/urupfu-rwa-alexia-mupende-rwashegeshe-benshi-mu-byamamare</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Alexia Mupende yari umunyamideli mpuzamahanga, wari uhagarariye  u [[Rwanda]], mu birori by'imyambarire yabereye i Kampala muri [[Uganda]], Geneve mu [[Ubusuwisi|busuwisi]], Dubai, United Arab Emirates, Colombo, Sri Lanka na Mumbai, mu [[Buhinde]]. Kugira ngo yongere amafaranga yinjiza, yabaye umuyobozi mukuru wa ''Waka Fitness'', club ya fitness mu mujyi wa [[Kigali]]. <ref name="2R">https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/200694</ref> <ref name="3R">https://www.softpower.ug/rwandas-celebrated-model-and-actress-alexia-mupende-killed-by-housemaid/</ref>

== Urupfu ==
Ku mugoroba wo ku wa kabiri, 8 Mutarama 2019, umurambo wa Alexia Uwera Mupende wabonetse muri kimwe mu byumba byo kuraramo kwa se mu Murenge wa Nyarugunga, [[Akarere ka Kicukiro|mu Karere ka Kicukiro]], mu nkengero z'umujyi wa [[Kigali]]. Yari yatewe icyuma inshuro nyinshi. <ref name="4R">https://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/top-rwandan-model-alexia-mupende-murdered</ref>

Abashinzwe umutekano mu [[Rwanda]] batangaje ko barimo gushakisha Antoine Niyireba, ufite imyaka 23, wari umukozi wo mu rugo kwa nyina wa nyakwigendera. Niwe wakekwagaho ubwicanyi. <ref name="5R">https://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/tributes-pour-model-alexia-mupende</ref>

== Ibindi bitekerezo ==
Igihe yapfaga, yasezeranye gushyingirwa muri Gashyantare 2019, kandi ubutumire bw'ubukwe bwari bwashyizwe ahagaragara. <ref name="6R">https://www.the-star.co.ke/news/2019/01/09/top-kenyan-born-rwandan-model-alexia-mupende-murdered_c1875377</ref> <ref name="7R">https://www.monitor.co.ug/News/World/Shock-top-Rwandan-model-Alexia-Mupende-murdered-house-maid/688340-4927094-lc8h36z/index.html</ref>

